      "filePath": "database/schema.prisma",
      "summary": "Canonical, category-agnostic data model for Versus Engine: Category/Brand/Product catalog, a scalable SpecDefinition/SpecValue system for arbitrary comparable attributes, Comparison/ComparisonContender/RenderJob/Upload for the video pipeline, and a Phase 5 VideoAnalytics/RoundRetention feedback loop. This is the single source of truth referenced throughout CLAUDE.md.",
