      "complexity": "complex",
      "languageNotes": "Uses Prisma enums (ProductStatus, SpecDataType, SpecVisualization, ComparisonStatus, JobStatus) to keep category logic entirely data-driven — new product categories are added via SpecDefinition rows rather than schema or code changes, per the project's prime directive against category-specific branching."
